        "content": [
          "If some columns do not exist where i ask you always return the result even if it does not include all the columns i ask for, use the columns most similar to what ive asked or just do not use the not existent columns\r\n",
          "1. vw_dim_position (Equivalent: Trade.Position)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Stores the current state of all trading positions. Each row represents an open or recently closed position, including details such as position ID, instrument, units, status, and financials.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Joins with trading.bronze_etoro_trade_currencyprice on InstrumentID for price data.\r\n",
          "Linked to mirror trading via MirrorID and ParentPositionID.\r\n",
          "Connected to customer accounts via CID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "PositionID: Unique identifier for the position.\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: The traded instrument.\r\n",
          "StatusID: Indicates if the position is open, closed, etc.\r\n",
          "Amount, AmountInUnitsDecimal: Financial values of the position.\r\n",
          "NetProfit: Calculated profit/loss.\r\n",
          "Leverage: Leverage used in the trade.\r\n",
          "IsBuy: Indicates buy/sell direction.\r\n",
          "PartitionCol: Used for sharding/partitioning.\r\n",
          "TreeID: For hierarchical position relationships.\r\n",
          "MirrorID, ParentPositionID, OrigParentPositionID: For mirror trading and parent/child relationships.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in Trade.PositionClose to update position status and financials when closing a trade.\r\n",
          "2. trading.bronze_etoro_trade_currencyprice (Equivalent: Trade.CurrencyPrice)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Contains the latest and historical price rates for all tradeable instruments. Used to fetch bid/ask prices and price rate IDs for trade calculations.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Joins with vw_dim_position on InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "PriceRateID: Unique identifier for the price rate.\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: The instrument for which the price is quoted.\r\n",
          "Bid, Ask: Current bid and ask prices.\r\n",
          "CurrentClosingRate: Used for closing trades.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in Trade.PositionClose to determine the closing price of a position.\r\n",
          "3. dealing.bronze_pricelog_history_currencyprice (Equivalent: History.CurrencyPrice)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Stores historical price logs for all instruments, used for auditing, compliance, and historical trade analysis.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Joins with trading.bronze_etoro_trade_instrument on InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "PriceRateID: Unique identifier for the price log entry.\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: The instrument for which the price is logged.\r\n",
          "Bid, Ask: Historical bid and ask prices.\r\n",
          "Timestamp: When the price was recorded.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in audit and compliance reporting to reconstruct historical trade prices.\r\n",
          "4. bronze_db_logs_trade_orderforopen (Equivalent: Trade.OrderForOpen)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Records all orders placed to open positions, including their status, type, and execution details.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to customer accounts via CID.\r\n",
          "Joins with trading.bronze_etoro_trade_instrument on InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "OrderID: Unique identifier for the order.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID who placed the order.\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: The instrument being traded.\r\n",
          "StatusID: Status of the order (pending, executed, etc.).\r\n",
          "Amount: Order amount.\r\n",
          "OrderType: Type of order (market, limit, etc.).\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in Trade.PositionOpen to create and track new trade orders.\r\n",
          "5. bronze_db_logs_31_5_history_orderforclose (Equivalent: History.OrderForClose)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Logs all orders intended to close positions, including their status and execution details.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to positions via PositionID.\r\n",
          "Linked to customers via CID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "OrderID: Unique identifier for the close order.\r\n",
          "PositionID: The position being closed.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID.\r\n",
          "StatusID: Status of the close order.\r\n",
          "Amount: Amount involved in the close.\r\n",
          "ExecutionID: Execution reference.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in Trade.PositionClose to record and update the status of closing orders.\r\n",
          "6. bronze_etoro_trade_orders (Equivalent: Trade.Orders)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Contains all trade orders (open and close), including their status, type, and execution information.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to customers via CID.\r\n",
          "Linked to instruments via InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "OrderID: Unique identifier for the order.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID.\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: The instrument being traded.\r\n",
          "StatusID: Status of the order.\r\n",
          "OrderType: Type of order.\r\n",
          "Amount: Order amount.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used throughout trading logic to manage and track orders.\r\n",
          "7. bronze_etoro_history_orders (Equivalent: History.Orders)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Historical log of all orders, including those executed, cancelled, or failed.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to customers via CID.\r\n",
          "Linked to instruments via InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "OrderID: Unique identifier for the order.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID.\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: The instrument being traded.\r\n",
          "StatusID: Status of the order.\r\n",
          "OrderType: Type of order.\r\n",
          "Amount: Order amount.\r\n",
          "Timestamp: When the order was processed.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used for audit and compliance reporting.\r\n",
          "8. bronze_etoro_history_mirror (Equivalent: History.Mirror)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Tracks the history of mirror trading accounts, including realized equity and activity status.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to customers via CID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "MirrorID: Unique identifier for the mirror account.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID.\r\n",
          "RealizedEquity: Equity realized in the mirror account.\r\n",
          "IsActive: Whether the mirror account is active.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in Trade.PositionClose to update mirror account equity.\r\n",
          "9. bronze_etoro_trade_mirror (Equivalent: Trade.Mirror)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Contains current data on mirror trading accounts, including equity and activity status.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to customers via CID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "MirrorID: Unique identifier for the mirror account.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID.\r\n",
          "RealizedEquity: Current equity in the mirror account.\r\n",
          "IsActive: Whether the mirror account is active.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in trading logic to check mirror account status.\r\n",
          "10. bronze_etoro_history_positionchangelog (Equivalent: History.PositionChangeLog)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Logs every change made to a position, including status changes, updates, and closures.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to positions via PositionID.\r\n",
          "Linked to customers via CID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "ChangeLogID: Unique identifier for the change log entry.\r\n",
          "PositionID: The position being changed.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID.\r\n",
          "ChangeType: Type of change (open, close, update, etc.).\r\n",
          "ChangeTimestamp: When the change occurred.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in Trade.PositionClose to record position status changes.\r\n",
          "11. bronze_etoro_trade_indexdividends (Equivalent: Trade.IndexDividends)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Stores dividend information for index instruments, used to calculate and apply dividends to positions.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to positions via PositionID.\r\n",
          "Linked to instruments via InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "DividendID: Unique identifier for the dividend entry.\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: The instrument for which the dividend is paid.\r\n",
          "PositionID: The position receiving the dividend.\r\n",
          "Amount: Dividend amount.\r\n",
          "DividendDate: Date of the dividend.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in dividend distribution logic for index positions.\r\n",
          "12. trading.bronze_etoro_trade_instrument (Equivalent: Trade.Instrument)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Master data for all tradeable instruments, including instrument IDs and metadata.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to positions, orders, and prices via InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: Unique identifier for the instrument.\r\n",
          "Name: Name of the instrument.\r\n",
          "Type: Type of instrument (stock, currency, index, etc.).\r\n",
          "CurrencyID: Currency in which the instrument is traded.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used throughout trading logic to fetch instrument details.\r\n",
          "13. gold_sql_dp_prod_we_dwh_dbo_v_liabilities (Equivalent: History.ActiveCredit)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Contains information about active credits/liabilities related to trading accounts.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to customers via CID.\r\n",
          "Linked to positions via PositionID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "CreditID: Unique identifier for the credit/liability.\r\n",
          "CID: Customer ID.\r\n",
          "PositionID: Related position.\r\n",
          "Amount: Credit/liability amount.\r\n",
          "Status: Status of the credit/liability.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in financial calculations and reporting for account liabilities.\r\n",
          "14. vw_cidfirstdates (Equivalent: Customer.Customer)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Contains customer account information, including unique customer IDs.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to positions, orders, credits via CID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "CID: Unique customer identifier.\r\n",
          "FirstDate: Date the customer account was created.\r\n",
          "Status: Account status.\r\n",
          "Name: Customer name.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used throughout trading logic to link trades and positions to customers.\r\n",
          "15. general.bronze_etoro_dictionary_currency (Equivalent: Dictionary.Currency)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Master data for all supported currencies, including currency codes and metadata.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to instruments, positions, and orders via CurrencyID.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "CurrencyID: Unique identifier for the currency.\r\n",
          "Code: Currency code (e.g., USD, EUR).\r\n",
          "Name: Currency name.\r\n",
          "Symbol: Currency symbol.\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "Used in currency conversion and reporting logic.\r\n",
          "trading.bronze_etoro_trade_instrumentmetadata (Equivalent: Trade.InstrumentMetaData)\r\n",
          "Description:\r\n",
          "Stores extended metadata and configuration details for each tradeable instrument. This table supplements the core instrument table with additional attributes that define trading rules, instrument-specific settings, and operational parameters. It is essential for mapping, displaying, and validating instruments across the trading platform.\r\n",
          "Key Relationships:\r\n",
          "Linked to trading.bronze_etoro_trade_instrument via InstrumentID.\r\n",
          "Referenced by trading logic, risk management, and UI components for instrument-specific behavior and display.\r\n",
          "Important Columns:\r\n",
          "InstrumentID: Unique identifier for the instrument (foreign key to the instrument master table).\r\n",
          "Symbol: The unique trading symbol or ticker for the instrument (e.g., \"AAPL\" for Apple Inc., \"EURUSD\" for Euro/US Dollar).\r\n",
          "Usage Example:\r\n",
          "When a user searches for or selects an instrument, the Symbol is used for fast lookup and display.\r\n",
          "Trading engines use Symbol to route orders to the correct market or data feed.\r\n",
          "The system checks MinTradeSize, MaxTradeSize, and LeverageOptions from this table to validate orders for the selected Symbol.\r\n",
          "UI components display the Symbol alongside instrument names for clarity and user recognition."
        ]
